OL,3,CAs Royal Mail issues warning over
OL,4,Ccounterfeit stamps, how do you spot a
OL,5,Cfake?
OL,7,FMembers of the public have complained
OL,8,Fthey have had to pay #5 penalties to
OL,9,Fcollect post because the stamps were
OL,10,Fdeemed to be counterfeit.
OL,12,FThe issue has emerged since the postal
OL,13,Fservice switched entirely to a new
OL,14,Fbarcoded system last July.
OL,16,FThe stamp on the left is genuine, the
OL,17,Fstamp on the right is counterfeit,
OL,18,Fwith the 'spiky' perforations.
OL,20,FHow do you spot a fake stamp?
