OL,3,CAs Royal Mail issues warning over
OL,4,Ccounterfeit stamps, how do you spot a
OL,5,Cfake?
OL,7,FRoyal Mail said: "Royal Mail takes the
OL,8,Fillegal production of counterfeit
OL,9,Fstamps seriously. Since the
OL,10,Fintroduction of barcoded stamps we
OL,11,Fhave been able to significantly reduce
OL,12,Fstamp fraud through added security
OL,13,Ffeatures.
OL,15,F"Every barcode is unique which allows
OL,16,Fus to identify whether a stamp is
OL,17,Fgenuine or not, and whether they have
OL,18,Fbeen previously used.
