OL,3,CAs Royal Mail issues warning over
OL,4,Ccounterfeit stamps, how do you spot a
OL,5,Cfake?
OL,7,F"We are working hard to remove
OL,8,Fcounterfeit stamps from circulation.
OL,9,FWe regularly monitor to detect
OL,10,Fsuspicious activity, such as sales of
OL,11,Fheavily discounted stamps and work
OL,12,Fclosely with retailers and law
OL,13,Fenforcement agencies to identify those
OL,14,Fwho produce counterfeit stamps.
