OL,3,CAs Royal Mail issues warning over
OL,4,Ccounterfeit stamps, how do you spot a
OL,5,Cfake?
OL,7,F"We have a robust, multistage process
OL,8,Fin place when assessing whether stamps
OL,9,Fare genuine. This includes a thorough
OL,10,Fexamination using specialist
OL,11,Fequipment, then a follow-up inspection
OL,12,Fby a skilled member of the team before
OL,13,Fany stamp is marked as counterfeit or
OL,14,Fpre-used."
